pageProduct.name: Accu-Chek Mobile Blood Glucose Meter Kit
pageProduct.description:
Information

NB The test strips for this machine are only subsidised for INSULIN dependant patients ONLY.

General Information

Get Mobile, stay mobile.
Whether you are at home or on the go bring your numbers to life with the Accu-Chek Mobile.

Features include:

  • 50 Strip Free tests on a continuous tape - no single strips to handle or dispose of (strips not included)
  • 6 lancets in a drum - no single lancets to see or touch
  • Easy lancing with 1-Click action to prime and release
  • Just 4 simple steps to perform a test
  • 2000 test memory plus 7, 14, 30 and 90 day averages
  • PC ready reports via a USB cable
  • Makes it easier to test on the go
